{"tid":653293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱出差雲南，見到一味好核突嘅餸......","createTime":"2018-05-04T14:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:58:30.000Z","uid":28938,"like":523,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f18b7a4ad84416515d958df26003b4fe6c28e3","tid":653293,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"今個星期代表公司捐錢去雲南某條村修橋，當地少數民族請我地成班人食飯，有一味餸係燒兔仔，我接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知個村民話唔係食兔仔，一刀劏開個兔仔肚，即刻跌左幾廿條肥菜蟲出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢一手揸幾條蟲仔擺落口，好似食朱古力咁滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我死都唔肯食，佢最後笑笑口無勉強我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7766477e8bbdbb31199e42edfa619a6a8b9b4457","tid":653293,"uid":167330,"like":114,"dislike":5,"score":109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"啲蟲係本身起個肚入面定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"85415b159b0800fc1b61990a1a0222b73a420483","tid":653293,"uid":57871,"like":284,"dislike":11,"score":273,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"雖然核突 但都想有圖"},{"pid":"847c8cbd1f30692ef1c1dc36619862963cecf2a2","tid":653293,"uid":52221,"like":125,"dislike":5,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"雲南蠱毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8fb868f267ef6b3d77dec5a38405912312d6bd","tid":653293,"uid":71166,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲蟲係本身起個肚入面定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放入阿兔個肚